OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778137534
OL,3,CMachete-wielding criminals jailed
OL,4,Cafter 'truly terrifying' burglary
OL,6,FThree men have been jailed after they
OL,7,Fcarried out a "truly terrifying"
OL,8,Fburglary in Hawkinge, Folkestone.
OL,10,FPolice were called to a house near
OL,11,FCorbett Road in November 2024, when
OL,12,Fburglars broke into the property
OL,13,Fwielding machetes.
OL,15,FThe victims, who were at home at the
OL,16,Ftime, heard a loud noise and came face
OL,17,Fto face with the masked offenders who
OL,18,Fhad forced their way inside.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
