FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778137534
OL,3,CMachete-wielding criminals jailed
OL,4,Cafter 'truly terrifying' burglary
OL,6,FThe burglars threatened the residents
OL,7,Fwith their weapons and demanded items,
OL,8,Fincluding watches and clocks, were
OL,9,Fhanded over to them. They then fled
OL,10,Fthe scene.
OL,12,FFollowing an investigation, police
OL,13,Ffound Callum Elliot, 23 and Darren
OL,14,FButler, 36, had broken into the house,
OL,15,Fwhilst wearing balaclavas and boiler
OL,16,Fsuits.
OL,18,FFurther investigations then revealed
OL,19,Fthat William Webb, 34, had planned the
OL,20,Fburglary, extensively researching the
OL,21,Fhouse they were targeting.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778137534
OL,3,CMachete-wielding criminals jailed
OL,4,Cafter 'truly terrifying' burglary
OL,6,FKent Police described the actions of
OL,7,Fthe three men as 'despicable' and
OL,8,F'cowardly'.
OL,10,FButler was jailed for eight years and
OL,11,Fseven months, Elliot was sentenced to
OL,12,Fseven years and two months'
OL,13,Fimprisonment, after both admitted to
OL,14,Faggravated burglary.
OL,16,FWebb was convicted for his involvement
OL,17,Fafter plotting to carry out the crime,
OL,18,Fin a unanimous jury verdict, and
OL,19,Fsentenced to three years and nine
OL,20,Fmonths behind bars.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
