OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778137534
OL,3,CMachete-wielding criminals jailed
OL,4,Cafter 'truly terrifying' burglary
OL,6,FInvestigating officer, Detective
OL,7,FConstable Holly Bayliss said: "The
OL,8,Fvictims in this case were subjected to
OL,9,Fa truly terrifying and traumatic
OL,10,Fordeal, and lives have been changed
OL,11,Fforever as a result of the despicable
OL,12,Factions of these cowardly offenders.
OL,14,F"I am very pleased that significant
OL,15,Fcustodial sentences have been handed
OL,16,Fdown to them, and I hope it will be of
OL,17,Fsome comfort to the victims to know
OL,18,Fthat those who targeted them in such a
OL,19,Fbrutal manner will spend a long time
OL,20,Fbehind bars.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
